moji\" />"},{"pid":"bb249dd9247c33057c5ce163d8bb4023af4832f4","tid":160318,"uid":68094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T16:11:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2e53112f88299cf97c9e80c1753b210c529dd1c2","tid":160318,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T17:37:32.000Z","msg":"bitcoin又爆泡沫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4ede8bd6b1374dc35ad2280f41240117e306f55","tid":160318,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T04:33:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ae2d00f22027190094f260b0dddf976d1d1e6ae","tid":160318,"uid":61589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T04:38:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點實名到? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係交易平台開戶口要實名?<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">落香港玩囉</span><br />\n<br />\n個BITCOIN WALLET VIRTUAL架<br />\n<br />\n海關都STOP唔到</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果現鈔搬到落香港<br />\n洗咩買bitcoin</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n現鈔不嬲都搬都黎香港<br />\n<br />\n你真係未見過支那人拖兩個行李喼既CASH去銀行存錢</blockquote><br />\n人地買bit coin目的都係想賣人仔買外匯走資<br />\n如果舊錢都落到黎香港，即係已經走左資喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲洗乜買bitcoin咁多此一舉？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"204fabdae6d53b8adfbbf1c1a166157a2723cdf9","tid":160318,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T07:14:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點實名到? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係交易平台開戶口要實名?<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">落香港玩囉</span><br />\n<br />\n個BITCOIN WALLET VIRTUAL架<br />\n<br />\n海關都STOP唔到</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果現鈔搬