like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T03:46:30.000Z","msg":"岩咪有BITCOIN 巴絲？<br />\n有無巴絲有BTC 想賣？<br />\n我今日想買BTC，用HKD 9，400 對 1 BTC 買。<br />\n幫幫手，THX~~<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e15d6b98fc6497ead4bb092ea21710e7a923b01","tid":160318,"uid":30039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T03:58:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>岩咪有BITCOIN 巴絲？<br />\n有無巴絲有BTC 想賣？<br />\n我今日想買BTC，用HKD 9，400 對 1 BTC 買。<br />\n幫幫手，THX~~<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\ntele: Btc98<br />\n詳談"},{"pid":"98587963bd257c1f3978cea3fb44eeb35e846e0b","tid":160318,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T16:35:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}